                    <h3 class="name centered">Paul F. Hamilton</h3>
                    
                    <p><span class="buisname">A Zappa Dappa Dat's</span> primary musician and songwriter, producer and engineer, audio consultant and technician, based at his studio in Illinois. Paul has been playing music since he was 9 years old, and has extensive experience with stage and studio sound production. He has opened for Johnny Cash, The Beach Boys, Linda Ronstadt, The Oak Ridge Boys, B.J. Thomas, Tanya Tucker, Brenda Lee, The Smothers Brothers, Mel Tillis, Ricky Skaggs, Roger Miller, Emmy Lou Harris, Ronnie Milsap, Marty Robbins, and many others.</p>
